ipe\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Recipe\">\n<h1 itemprop=\"name\">Peppermint Bark</h1>\n<div class=\"socialButtons\">\n<div class=\"fb-like\" data-send=\"false\" data-href=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/peppermint-bark/\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"105\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-action=\"like\"></div>\n<div class=\"pinterest\">\n<a href=\"http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com%2Frecipes%2Fpeppermint-bark%2F&media=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com/recipes/peppermint-bark/peppermint-bark_large.jpg&description=Peppermint%20Bark\" class=\"pin-it-button\" count-layout=\"horizontal\">Pin It</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"print\"><a href=\"/pdfs/peppermint-bark.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Peppermint Bark');\"><img src=\"/img/icons/print.png\" alt=\"Print\" /></a><a href=\"/pdfs/peppermint-bark.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Peppermint Bark');\">Print or download (PDF)</a></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n<li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/\">Recipes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/desserts/\"><span itemprop=\"recipeCategory\">Desserts</span></a></li>\n<li>Peppermint Bark</li>\n</ul>\n<div itemprop=\"description\" class=\"description\">A delicious holiday treat that's even better with a big mug of hot chocolate.</div>\n<div class=\"stats\">\n<ul>\n<li>Prep: <meta itemprop=\"prepTime\" value=\"PT25M\"/>25 min</li>\n<li>Chill: <meta itemprop=\"chillTime\" value=\"PT1H\"/>1 hour</li>\n<li>Total: <meta itemprop=\"totalTime\" value=\"PT1H25M\"/>1 hour 25 min</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeYield\">Yields 2 pounds bark</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"steps\">\n<div class=\"right\">\n<a href=\"/recipes/peppermint-bark/peppermint-bark_large.jpg\"><img class=\"polaroid\" src=\"/recipes/peppermint-bark/peppermint-bark.jpg\" alt=\"Peppermint Bark\" itemprop=\"image\"/></a>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"direction\">Line a 13x9 inch baking pan with wax paper.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 pound semi-sweet baking chocolate or milk chocolate, chopped</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">In a double boiler, melt chocolate, stirring frequently, until smooth.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Pour chocolate into lined baking pan.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 pound white baking chocolate squares, chopped</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">In a double boiler, melt white chocolate, stirring frequently, until smooth.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 teaspoon peppermint extract (optional)</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Stir extract into white chocolate until combined.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Slowly pour white chocolate over semi-sweet chocolate on baking sheet. Swirl chocolates together with a knife.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac12; cup peppermint candy canes, crushed</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Sprinkle chocolate with crushed candy. Chill until firm, about one hour or longer.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Use wax paper to lift bark from baking sheet; break into pieces. Store tightly covered at room temperature.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"footnote\">\n<div class=\"logo\">MakeBetterFood.com</div>\nFrom MakeBetterFood.com. <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2012-12-10\">Dec 10, 2012</time>. (http://makebetterfood.com/recipes/peppermint-bark/). Adapted from <a href='http://www.christmas-cookies.com/recipes/recipe552.swirledpeppermintbark.html'>Christmas-Cookies.com</a>.\n</div>\n<!-- Microformat Ingredients -->\n<ul class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 pound semi-sweet baking chocolate or milk chocolate, chopped</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 pound white baking chocolate squares, chopped</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 teaspoon peppermint extract (optional)</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac12; cup peppermint candy canes, crushed</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Microformat Steps -->\n<ol class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Line a 13x9 inch baking pan with wax paper.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">In a double boiler, melt chocolate, stirring frequently, until smooth.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Pour chocolate into lined baking pan.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">In a double boiler, melt white chocolate, stirring frequently, until smooth.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Stir extract into white chocolate until combined.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Slowly pour white chocolate over semi-sweet chocolate on baking sheet. Swirl chocolates together with a knife.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Sprinkle chocolate with crushed candy. Chill until firm, about one hour or longer.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Use wax paper to lift bark from baking sheet; break into pieces. Store tightly covered at room temperature.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<h4>Related Equipment or Ingredients</h4>\n<div class=\"pushTop10 clearfix polarioidSummaryRow\">\n<div class=\"polaroidSummary\">\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Wear-Ever-Natural-Finish-Aluminum-4x12-7/dp/B0001MS3P6?SubscriptionId=AKIAJT76QZNN5CAIGPSQ&tag=makbetfoo-20&linkCode=xm2&camp=2025&creative=165953&creativeASIN=B0001MS3P6\"><img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/21Zmyou77JL.SL100_AA105.jpg\" alt=\"Rimmed Baking Sheet\" class=\"\"/>\nRimmed Baking Sheet</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<div class=\"grid_2 alpha\">\n<img src=\"/img/cookbook/cover_bestof_grid3.png\" alt=\"Best of Make Better Food\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 138px; width:100%;\" class=\"dropShadow\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_10 omega\">\n<h4>Get New Recipes via Email + Free Cookbook</h4>\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n<form action=\"http://makebetterfood.us5.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=23bb9cd41955f33d8db8c9e91&amp;id=f2cac69129\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=